last_episode_to_air.name: Hearth and Home
last_episode_to_air.overview: Ellie steps up to emcee a funeral on Dean's behalf. Gwen and Stu hash out their differences. Sharyn tries yum cha, Beau launches a new venture, and Bradley finally delivers.

name: Good Grief
overview: Two very different sisters inherit a funeral home - and its eccentric employees - from their koro. While Ellie is determined to uphold her grandfather's legacy, Gwen can't wait to get to Bali and become a DJ. Can they figure out their lives while staring death in the face?

episodes.name: A Matter of Life and Death: Part One
episodes.overview: A pair of very different sisters inherit a funeral home, complete with its eccentric employees, from their koro. Gwen is intent on going to Bali to become a DJ, but Ellie wants to uphold their grandfather's legacy.

episodes.name: A Matter of Life and Death: Part Two
episodes.overview: Ellie and Gwen infiltrate a funeral at a competitor mortuary, which goes horribly wrong. Ellie tells Gwen she doesn't want to sell the business.

episodes.name: Face Off
episodes.overview: Ellie attempts to manage the crew's expectations; Gwen learns about techniques on how to apply mortuary makeup.

episodes.name: Missed Connections
episodes.overview: A bogan family want Loving Tributes to provide a medium so that their deceased mother can plan her own funeral. Sharyn is happy to help.

episodes.name: Sick Puppies
episodes.overview: The funeral for a handsome young man leads to an unexpected group of unwelcome guests to the mortuary.

episodes.name: Heart Attack
episodes.overview: Ellie decides to bring the staff to a health and safety course, which turns out to be neither healthy nor safe.

episodes.name: Don't Worry, Be Happy
episodes.overview: Ellie's attempt to rebrand herself and Loving Tributes receives some pushback from the new co-owner, Dean; Beau has picked up other work; Sharyn enjoys a hamper.

episodes.name: Play Nice
episodes.overview: Gwen is forced to stay at Ellie's house after being kicked out of home by their mum. Dean offers a discount to some clients, Beau freestyles, and Sharyn looks like Margot Robbie.

episodes.name: Tragedy Plus Time
episodes.overview: Gwen pranks Maia's new boyfriend, while a stressed Ellie tries to convince Dean she will fall in line. Beau does some life modelling, and Sharyn recommends a plumber.

episodes.name: Hot Water
episodes.overview: Gwen and Beau have an early morning call-out, and Ellie feels guilty about her outburst. The staff film a TV advert, to Dean's delight, and Sharyn hosts a 'Spa-BQ'.

episodes.name: Empty Nest
episodes.overview: Ellie and Kobe get to work in the bathroom; Gwen helps a client plan a funeral; Beau offers life advice; Sharyn has a new robot.
